威克氏族被认为是三代成功的故事 - 直到父子冲突揭示出令人惊讶的裂痕。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="text_block block-3" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="pad" style="padding-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-top: 10px;"&gt;&lt;div style="font-family: sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;div class="class" style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial,'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #555; line-height: 1.2;"&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px;"&gt;多年来， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=d545b26246ba4f02a151df7672fa7441&amp;amp;_e=ioWwAoR3rPjTBzMmKHGfU38jzEAwRCfTyns80LBzxy4KnukXUPgNgLnwHpXRRyKge6Q7Dsk5uuWVr9jT_T68jd__9hcpHJgfYSoIoDrWG4u2-NWeL6lDl2hoR1YAydCsUJR1___5uPN9SHmhU7uxxR41UpnE9AVdQLLmHuzhYa491LehZCL3E6OWt_HXQC58g8n1-mt4az9pFEfVdQMscLWJwdKYRho1RbWJVwy637mSdjOd4oP4ufYA7Ly9R8QkN-W8HuWMPP1tLbD19BcP9_w-KJwziXUuEX0rty9CpskpJx-Rvtm-zxiRNq5nTxaqm-MFgf-yPBoaZvp3suVz0PPBxAtb5DYYwn7v682MkSU4Gqtu_q3vWDQ9Wv0YbNiS2y_Esacv6VsRNe_-c6LMWX2OEAQuWROV4nF6uCX0f76JKUKgw6PSmYaGC0XG29rm3Q8cUQXbVWQAErLCxecv001mqoxdwiWHmPRj2wer3yVhLNIlykY1FYx0MpjmWcPxdmu0w7Eohg1UeF2yxspcZR45FpXGoSM9UjkCW8g4Z_obOrwQ2LdAW0-877geXWUgfcHemTfC6oM9TdGmw37cjHQAKXf8gWJuk38VY8xk4K-GvLkIy1J4s2VqbPdNqyB_om4LhOxISZ2N0LlmyZ3_iR8TpqAZyuVQ3zoZGfAzKMDmny_VAV_FNOK4RM1hLcyr0XmaPht52sEqWebqk4ouvKp3_3IW5Kxsk4xq1uq5uQveO0dy_1ZSHT_zJFhq3ULK5Ujjua7vslzVumW2yXtu2Whr7UvM9F866zf6mS5Rccc%3D" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #000000;" target="_self"&gt;新加坡最富有的家庭&lt;/a&gt;看起来像是有效的继任计划的典范。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px;"&gt;最近的一场父子仇恨破坏了这一形象，并将170亿美元的Kwek氏族变成了一个警告性的故事，为家庭控制公司的投资者。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px;"&gt;世界各地的富裕家庭正准备将数万亿个继承人传给其继承人。在亚洲，许多老化的大亨正在努力努力将其商业王朝的ins绳交给其后代，还是雇用外部专业人员来管理它们。 Kweks的传奇是从对20个人，文件和公开声明的访谈中拼凑而成的，它表明，即使是最精心编排的领导型转变也可以通过不信任和对不良商业决策的指控来颠覆。&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="button_block block-4" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="pad" style="padding-bottom: 15px; padding-top: 15px; text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;div align="left" class="alignment"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=d545b26246ba4f02a151df7672fa7441&amp;amp;_e=ioWwAoR3rPjTBzMmKHGfU38jzEAwRCfTyns80LBzxy4KnukXUPgNgLnwHpXRRyKge6Q7Dsk5uuWVr9jT_T68jd__9hcpHJgfYSoIoDrWG4u2-NWeL6lDl2hoR1YAydCsUJR1___5uPN9SHmhU7uxxR41UpnE9AVdQLLmHuzhYa491LehZCL3E6OWt_HXQC58g8n1-mt4az9pFEfVdQMscLWJwdKYRho1RbWJVwy637mSdjOd4oP4ufYA7Ly9R8QkN-W8HuWMPP1tLbD19BcP9_w-KJwziXUuEX0rty9CpskpJx-Rvtm-zxiRNq5nTxaqm-MFgf-yPBoaZvp3suVz0PPBxAtb5DYYwn7v682MkSU4Gqtu_q3vWDQ9Wv0YbNiScWGPc5GZ1yh0Q0aryP5VSx7oH2X5XHklqQZ4posxM3ikzbQhk8Y2WaBIZuEdCspd__8-WqTA_rB94kJ_1VrRrrmJnOGRYVOz2EvxDOOMuWC7g-YxfpwY2ppezvT8rWmX5gHXyRN8IOstzDAZCL73sBkae5HCyqJU2GqPUy6Q2LaCo9HP5HdDnynFhM1xkwx6RUOZCr37J5KCAoN7fGcGim3OkjDnbV34U5IgRLlyYerCxlGvDz4WglcGqdqIDgg69FwDvOK8Sl_P_8GAzVkyLfmR07jSx-Z58tHg_ihy1tbN_C6oMFLBlk6TRB3zp_iqBGcfjhk14fVS5dginHhGl9eZesEgX3sW_CK6s4xVd2J-kzp6E3oRxNOxJKFsqrsttRg9QqM4JCfipTKDrXIN9tgFAhAAtD2M4aVjZ9fAv2c%3D" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;v:roundrect xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;_m=d545b26246ba4f02a151df7672fa7441&amp;_e=ioWwAoR3rPjTBzMmKHGfU38jzEAwRCfTyns80LBzxy4KnukXUPgNgLnwHpXRRyKge6Q7Dsk5uuWVr9jT_T68jd__9hcpHJgfYSoIoDrWG4u2-NWeL6lDl2hoR1YAydCsUJR1___5uPN9SHmhU