sQCf4nkUPiMoBi1az5X19KMG8FmBSBue0bBbyJYDzNnXfwn5OL1XKwFWBBjJ3hh2NBQv0Dj1MFnZAEycGFhCn1gSkOoIMA3GMD4aL5pyRXHhaIIgd23s_2WH9X2zvTDton-X8gIEA1C6W4hoJMR5s6lH2cdRdt82uRC64kY_9gxfVvoM1Sqy9aHga2OCv6D8KdFUfdElTHgmO4lOGScRs1ezYJ8QqL7ATkCLxNtiePBWaUly1pf2PNkck_mpNWaw-hAFWRGO-eaqM/U0Pi4FogQcTCTAYJYtyPGji81biIHx1X/8" target="_blank"&gt;优先考虑几乎没有美国人会声称的税收减免&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;推高前购物&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国消费者的三月&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7WJZxfZaI5uMV55KxTjKej9Op8w5N6O7GhLExdGl1jiawlK1topmSHZcbTADgiqr5QqMvR3opG_USJZJyKjLupLaTKCYovn1My4X3fYwUec7CD6cZN37dCl9t3Kuir9D7vPwM2huXTc-56HKirMFSmsOtduHrKYeQn76RT4qAJeaoqk7wQP4CYzAKlFbx54UI7O-lCvGdcflRMtdMyrWeDFzR7Vmrpsy0b15psDXv_d7tejvgYjnxsm5i_IQCYNCs1GxXcZOOrPkHdvJQ5rNoIr1NKBGDzJRE7heBSCmLUSzeS5QUanMXDFV5Ht4RBn3S9kdNNq-tF9jQ5jF9v-zE7HdWWM4pcVhtrgjcQtLd8ozqSOvd4oytkz6LAA/JiVrMXphLQ280oNM-GGkRJpxxBsW4XHR/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;购物狂潮&lt;/a&gt;将在第一季度拯救经济。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;受到高关税的威胁，这肯定会在接下来的几个月中提高价格，美国人购买了汽车，电子产品以及通常从中国进口的运动配件等物品类型。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;上个月，零售销售的涨幅证实了轶事证据表明，现在急于购买，而不是后来访问&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Fo1S0_3Kj-ef8jhNOHMQ1q-BRI6w3gbtyQst-hYSH11qNcSntVEFHfmmD1d46r-hkiOaiF6TJAXqxrxG772a3enszMgs-6L-iW3446akL0Pv-wxsnvZ87XMfPgme72Uzkr3XRNBeWSpzg-_3KwFmw2X_ujlaakG9aSs_fHEJ3xleHk71DUbZrlpEt_1pxxrBPrXWQ8H1ErV2b3vM89nLN9Ri1gzseSYj3c-GG7Sj3Ca2X-m8Bwsknmh9gV1-wcSjzpvzquOsu4IBAFjIKT4kgsPuVg4HaNgUolcdTrH98UhxRbKlVvK6tqcm86qI8yB_Af7Ds7rGYPCA8fAqfgd3hS_hKcvM_128UEmY1-FwKbnDjXtoZyDkwA-xmqQ/QUUPIUxlNm5wphJGLgMlEKuvMAmFdjTM/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;汽车经销店&lt;/a&gt;的任何人都可以见证。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifGQgq3Bzp7Y/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifGQgq3Bzp7Y/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;令人惊讶的提升也是提升第一季度经济活动的估计。现在，亚特兰大美联储的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9SrdqOOYbgISr0QGuuPM9TR4KcE65cqq8ixi_ADUXSJDjkFejr1MwLPGCLQlK9WRc9p7D80V43wWaEklwadHgZzR_vMifA821oEYJ-AeuyRA4X4745ncJ4mkflLZ_7hRg-gftP2atIN0a8aeiUfRJspzDvryHMqUSxHgAd1OjKh9mEpWQ6N3HqlSqLIRmQ1a_FwbmPaQ0kC9wJrxVpqU9sQ4DAuZ6tkwbSGTf-JiLfvzcyK5gWK_uUDVp6TNlsduO9GotWL_lLYfG1LTVHBrNAlm6lbHkwsG6MpzZ-SxcHe7cetItmicIb5QC__Wfyiqp0SY4wfm8KNIcX54uUAHQLZgCYwFiATBfSgP0uwhKpni-CvLSdldcumvsDhTWU0uMwFotTQ9zGfoeNbz37B99DPVzHgYbc9kA_Vtcp990jGACb2BPGqI55POOGwt3A/eQaefFSlEWNtdSfZgybwP_KB2ZHCvSWm/8" target="_blank" title="gdpnow"&gt;GDPNOW&lt;/a&gt;预测仅显示出0.1％的下降 - 不包括黄金贸易的影响 - 比几周前预测的较大下降更好的结果。包括&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XyINk1ibe135I4TiO2mbk5VLWQyZ3PAUVAPJgK3xlPBfNauZ1W3l7l2pNqh9PQbHlT_uJkFVLgE5mSQVz1-njKtEy5rXPn91Bn5eLuqLdXHKXU_E5hXgfHEP-sBZDaOD-aKkl2CDorGzvRCmwvhuScv6VGX3X0gKMt_zokBOi_Lv1550iHi0d7peHY31iG3sFJ9rVQtxEGXlvujFAE4Vko3hVVwBE1KDrX8PzFeoEFDRjweNJs9o84eJrkEnsnN98X0vqKcT38h2wzmwTJ_KJDAQtd8MP8w-rzy_6oil72c0Dg_wjp5chQmx5UyHSRB3z9fdYTr8Rl1VdtKJpoBby0QUPUI5XI-GbuyZpNPOEv11eY10zlXWK2jGM02B3Uo4ltmAaPRfIM2p7c1bWZ6oh6xtw3_EwSt_qu0m04Pa5vJNeCl585sGAbHk5RRJwIM8JGA4EjiekSSX_AQozQFoBC-8IJdAMK4uzQ4pfj1ISedsVqWrD_xhOd6hczO5zNuZRuo8zcwUe3uuE1GlzSL12mx2l2dg8TQetb_JmSDC1sBTkn0JN9hwsnh7A0nB_OiCZqhTaZisnqJszfzwqJVEpg7XZiKXGrplD9DWY1fZ_bSDrcSGN7FbrusnI_-jE6U4plc-OJ9vcDcavwWfsvsxlnv7