 16px 0;"&gt;美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）在芝加哥经济俱乐部的一次活动上发表讲话， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7KSqQBFoATaQD7YYz78heE_Z3F631Q4V07SYnyp9NxJT6JmDkQQlK4qde8hde3jF1147w3oTaec1o52saNw2_zGOjE3enhAvUhjrPGYNg23DL_hi_IHkS6-PKZ0xgEdNj2Fy-kgqLLwx-xq2gWMAwwksBq8IQ4rqlqsDrWTrr4PoLdIK4g4XN9C7VOJUklD49ZyH5QUA5QrvmKiZugn5NTLlqXV4U10XnDPJhtRlAhXrQ3PkG1vZONg_5imwRMQWagbFIWRw7N5bdX70M_D5053FwDWczgPob_TesW7R-_996L-3p6fw1wFlmEEzPBoESCVDHfLrHAlQfAnruCj1bzVauKwGh3zHmj92AS8lSuosH_J4ZU2f2enX7gU/Dr37hrDZI4K0U3xOu8RE3aPfU3qqUqP4/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;他承认&lt;/a&gt;，经济疲软和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/X0nfjSbqN9AloqFM6mP_B8Yfov-kgsjvG3Dr8WdUk2HcUzT66MkE-DgOIKI_4r7WThqgveQA-XTfT4S3WUwNl5YRYuzvH3zUOR5pwjGS_E3eNhDoNNiHt7sXdZDgvK4fqkvyUGjyax5KIjF6oUk_Z3QN1LUfuDDpUM-vv6toULvSMvgIQNezDhjWKtcaHOmyerLz5bJgMtH8AlkcgvuKJihs-4z4QLCAyX8XdEoRZIhjouIYVuNwqPYWq5sxYJhSvp_zK9beQv7uVo_WYhbeugAX1u5oxA3pepv0PeuIncZ55VDaE-V78fQEHrTgX6EVh7-Seb3mJ9mNAIQMxgFZfZNB51-QFkmn3O13TrSvNIr92LBt0oxhruHLOd4/D--gFkgsv3N2r521apG2QQTHMoxMk-xG/8" target="_blank"&gt;通货膨胀率提高&lt;/a&gt;最终可能会使中央银行的两个目标陷入冲突。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; Pantheon宏观经济学在一份Netstore中写道：“我们认为，随着关税与实际收入的关税率和更大的经济不确定性对支出有效的打击，消费将有效地停滞不前。” &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SodoHqlkAdWY2u39xfIKKJd6svh4wFeWdwOu3W1pznYsFbFOXVGrbG-l6uh9CQQH3SzdvAXJYZc2thUgYa7LXZVvX0fwQf05pKbK8tl6HwqbUsmQmfWIXf1qEWiOXAgqFgs70RsUgZhGp7Q2qb7S1NvrqrMz0gWyvOwqpQbmqz2a7vSAclM0Y-nGr-8A2F7Zrgg72jRFtJbGkEaK56m0G6jpsZaiQEpxGvL1kVrIRh6gN0h_bjGAjndO-gtk_a4Ulileq7m2LHdAz25c72YD7qcUXR4fuLZyL2dnNd0BXu92bkJFmbO1WClTKiwQTvjbbn5yS3nmLvbEY7dkas78X4M_aKb4-9LOY9MlJaYBtDMq9bIf2fSfu8hPoAFaXp0IQVcS93Ze3OrqAKvhU7v-TCLGWzChdmtMWT12JG90ndaAjLUOvj2aaZcJQ_EgBi4Vt__bqT7smXGo7RrnymgHlFfu71Uim24lH8uUzKlGZRKLMkf-G2XdweW12PSxO5iEwhqF8dEas7odT2