family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;年轻的选民在即将举行的加拿大大选中至关重要&lt;/strong&gt;，而党的领导人正在竞赛，以确保他们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jGpPN9cnALSHMfi_oFsoygiuqWDaTFgSgat-OzFM8RNLDbyFR8TXlBRc3ivGtfbXOpnLIAgUz9eWn-ZWq_RfXy6NLzQzY8cbvJos0gkd7WMMA_74NBtpW0xHa8w1UquferbfqVnFEtnmWpEQGt7Bgj96cslDvwBWWmFjVVzRASMN37EJj6ngBdoAVPXjGRWcb1CZa6ssmuQb2GZM4_8pICqrQQ0P20Vy_yXpAou9MXLH6lgs0XE3EDcr86CSt1H0KgmT-I-Hb5n1cFbtehKM2KMyIau-7KBdqvX7MTKbqKg3FtUbBxJKe5wYQLPi4mN_VnbJ5AktLWK6pTObXCYRLDkT7XmBlYECy-LQKgh2EUDs-EXlED255hFEWtc/01L1wNmTKq7JgMZ566bTUuBrvQsu0sRl/8" target="_blank"&gt;最热情的人口统计资料&lt;/a&gt;在民意测验中出现。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一项新的调查&lt;/strong&gt;使这两个主要政党在18至34岁的选民中基本上捆绑在一起，加拿大年轻人指出通货膨胀和特朗普的关税和侵略性，因为最高问题影响了他们的投票。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;年轻人特别&lt;/strong&gt;倾向于保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）。据Nanos Research称，妇女支持&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/03YVJ2eJxWwd1G4evzt4MCRF0h44Ltx5rUOXVl6z7oZu9if3wh-VW1eDUF7UHbSbS8f1tEkpIpVhIAzZEiHtHoHwqWCCxkNYFsuYU3Kxz-gfZRGhgdEKRhDAmCm-JO3oVuJ8BcRczkaade9G0EIJz52O8vuR_Yv4UYpPcRwBReGaprO77ad9dA_FL4rI3ABhv2Lmlzc80ykdeUVMoALroA1Fxmt0iS18wmZiqhO5RKWuZGddRFKAFiYlnF2yzZRqdaeL4o1avtG9TPEED7J510xGfwAJVlPe4_FACoNt7c-suFKqblHIpTqScUWg89ZGscLpGWF4hnkyg1-8v5v-J4_khlsuambkQPLPE0iorClXd-v1pU4s3ilEuSM/soscmfr3nZWD1YAgkCIiyGemK23eUgoB/8" target="_blank"&gt;马克·卡尼的自由党的&lt;/a&gt;两倍多。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tD0TY-mgV1n4WEyX4I0Bcpd69JeQEwzo3JhG3rag0_g2K1351UpfwRzzjNg0-EUO2HmLoXgMC3DAkKLjAOFAokvXs-MAGDEC3JJbCVM9vgznu_QE2aKbbjgn5qVUi-j-ccmcMRHh9d2O777ruLRKoDPBCnKoEBnZf1sx6isLNkqchbjrxV2FtZz2W5rbz-FEjOKpTEVQ0SsCyia-FWhNfjSDyq